.TP 8n
\f[I]message_size\fP
The size in bytes of the location in which to store the returned message.
.TP 8n
\f[I]fildes\fP
The original fildes, exactly as passed to the \f[I]fchdir\fP(2) system call.
.\" ------------------------------------------------------------------------
